# 1. Do you have any hobbies?

Yes, quite a few actually. Since I’m a computer science student, I spend a lot of my free time coding and learning about AI technologies, which is both my major and my hobby. Apart from that, I’m really into competitive programming because I enjoy solving challenging algorithm problems. To relax, I also like listening to music and going for walks, especially when I’ve been studying for a long time. I think hobbies are important because they help me stay mentally balanced and motivated.

### 中文翻译：

有的，其实我有不少爱好。因为我是计算机专业学生，所以我空闲时间会花很多时间写代码、学习人工智能相关技术，这既是我的专业，也是我的兴趣爱好。除此之外，我也很喜欢算法竞赛，因为我很享受解决复杂算法问题的过程。为了放松，我还喜欢听音乐和散步，特别是在长时间学习之后。我觉得兴趣爱好很重要，因为它们能让我保持心理平衡和动力。

---

# 2. Did you have any hobbies when you were a child?

Definitely. When I was a child, I was really fond of outdoor activities, especially playing basketball and riding bicycles with my friends after school. I also spent a lot of time playing video games, which probably explains why I later became interested in computers and technology. Compared with now, my hobbies were simpler and more entertainment-oriented, while nowadays I prefer hobbies that can also improve my skills or broaden my knowledge.

### 中文翻译：

当然有。我小时候特别喜欢户外活动，尤其是放学后和朋友一起打篮球、骑自行车。我那时候也花了很多时间玩电子游戏，这大概也是后来我对电脑和科技产生兴趣的原因。相比现在，我小时候的爱好更加简单，也更偏向娱乐；而现在我更喜欢那些既能放松又能提升技能、拓宽知识面的兴趣。

---

# 3. Do you have the same hobbies as your family members?

To some extent, yes, but we also have quite different interests. For example, my father enjoys reading news and watching documentaries, and I sometimes do the same because I like learning about technology and current events. However, my hobbies are much more related to computers and AI, which my parents are not very familiar with. On the other hand, we all enjoy spending time together during holidays, such as traveling or having family dinners, so I think we share some lifestyle hobbies rather than exactly the same personal interests.

### 中文翻译：

在某种程度上是的，不过我们也有不少不同的兴趣。比如我父亲喜欢看新闻和纪录片，而我有时候也会这样做，因为我喜欢了解科技和时事。不过，我的爱好更多和电脑以及人工智能有关，而我父母对这些并不太熟悉。另一方面，我们一家人都喜欢在假期一起相处，比如旅行或者家庭聚餐，所以我觉得我们更多是共享一些生活方式上的兴趣，而不完全是相同的个人爱好。
